| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1592 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ed4b252-ff79-57f2-9a34-2519e541bd04"
